# DevOps/SRE own the higher environments only — every PR touching beta or the
# production regions requires their review. GitHub enforces code-owner review
# solely on PRs whose changed files match a pattern below.
#
# staging is deliberately NOT owned: onboarding a service, the CI image-
# automation lane, and staging env-var tweaks all touch only apps/staging/**,
# apps/base/**, clusters/staging/**, service-registry/** and catalog/** — none
# of which are listed here — so staging self-service merges without a required
# review. A base-values change reaches production only through an (owned)
# Enable Environment / prod PR.
/apps/beta/**       @duynhne
/apps/prod-us/**    @duynhne
/apps/prod-eu/**    @duynhne
/clusters/prod/**   @duynhne
CODEOWNERS          @duynhne
